name: Agent
line: What's up Rick!

name: Rick
line: What's the matter with you Morty?

name: Agent
line: You're always picking on me. You're so petty.

name: Rick
line: Oh, my God! He's trying to tell us something.  That's so awesome.

name: Agent
line: It's not my job to take sides or pass judgment. You do the same thing, and we're both adults that want what's best for our son.

name: Rick
line: Then why aren't you helping him, Jerry?

name: Agent
line: Because he's not me. He's my partner. And I don't really care about anyone's feelings.

name: Rick
line: You don't have to be mean, sweetie.

name: Agent
line: Aw, fuck.

name: Rick
line: Look, I know you're frustrating me, but it's better than making my problems other people's problems.

name: Agent
line: Okay, fine. I'll talk to you later.

name: Rick
line: Yeah, okay.

name: Agent
line: I understand your feelings. I understand your anger. But, uh, I don’t think it’s necessary to keep talking about this. You know, if I were to talk about it, I think you might get sick of your life.

name: Rick
line: Shut up, Jerry. You’re an animal.

name: Agent
line: If I were you, I wouldn’d eat more vegetables.

name: Rick
line: Jerry, stop saying that! Stop saying that. You are making my pee problem.

name: Agent
line: Listen!

name: Rick
line: You’ve obviously never put enough pressure on yourself to get that pickle to make it work.

name: Agent
line: All right, all right, Morty. All right, take these seeds are gonna be good for my precious pheromone.

name: Rick
line: That’m…

name: Agent
line: You know what a pheros are for ants?
